(295, 1, '2018-04-26 12:59:00', '2018-04-26 12:59:00', '<strong>Hours</strong>\r\n\r\nOur winter hours (until April 30th) are 10am - 3pm, closed sundays.\r\nOur spring - fall hours (May 1st - October 1st) are 8am to 45 minutes before sunset\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>Range Addresses:</strong>\r\n\r\nWe currently have two ranges:\r\n\r\n        <strong>Outdoor Range</strong>\r\n	<li> 24 Reeves Road, \r\n             New Glasgow, NS,\r\n             B2H 5C7</li>\r\n<div class=\"map\">kkkkkk</div>\r\n\r\n        <strong>Indoor Range</strong>\r\n        <li> 40 Foster Ave, \r\n             Stellarton, NS,\r\n             B0K 1S0</li>\r\n\r\nWe rent the indoor range on sundays from the first sunday in december until the last in april. It is open from 12pm - 5pm.\r\n\r\nOur indoor range will take up to 9mm and 38 special calibers. No magnum rounds and no .177.\r\n\r\nOur outdoor range has a 25 and 100 yard firing line and will accomodate up to a 303 calibur (50 cal. black powder) on the 100 yard line. Handguns and 22 calibers are permitted on the 25 yard line. Note that we are not certified for holster shooting at this time.', 'Range Information', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '70-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-04-26 12:59:00', '2018-04-26 12:59:00', '', 70, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2018/04/26/70-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
